import React from 'react' import { useState, useEffect } from 'react' function UserHomepage(currentUser, setCurrentUser) { const [userData, setUserData] = useState([]) useEffect(() => { fetch('/user-homepage') .then(response => response.json()) .then(data => { setUserData(data) }) }, []) return (

Welcome, {userData.name}

{userData.username}

Location: {userData.location}

Member since: {userData.date_joined}

Camera Equipment: {userData.camera}

Editing Software: {userData.editing}

Light Kit: {userData.lights}

Audio Equipment: {userData.audio}

Props: {userData.props}

) } export default UserHomepage
